 the incident interstellar\nradiation field (ISRF). Using models of dust and the ISRF in the literature we\nillustrate that the predicted brightness is indeed lower, though not as faint\nas the observations indicate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 May 2023 10:23:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-02"}
